The quest of three old shelves, which could be the key of a strange and worrying enigma, leds Edward Carnby and Aline Cedrac on the shadow island.
But hardly have they land than they discover mysterious creatures of evil. On this island where terror reigns, behind each shadow can be dissimulated uncredible secrets like atrocious nightmares...

